name: WorldTop10News
skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: sath's top news
des:
Get the latest news from World Top 10 News now on Alexa. 
Follow the latest news and breaking news around the world. Stay Up to date on weather, entertainment, politics and health from Top 10 News updated hourly. World Top 10 News keeps you in the know.

After enabling this skill, invoke the app by saying: "Alexa, start sath's top news"

Intents: 
Yes - to read out the news for you
No - if not required.
Help -> to get instructions on how to use the skill.
quit/exit/close -> to exit from the skill.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
